ded-catalyst-turns-co%e2%82%82-and-waste-into-fertilizer-at-industrially-relevant-rates</link><description>新加坡国立大学 (NUS) 的研究人员开发了一种计算引导策略，可以更有效地利用二氧化碳和硝酸盐生产尿素。通过结合大语言模型、密度泛函理论计算和实验，该方法确定了一种镉改性氧化铁催化剂，该催化剂在实际电流密度下保持高尿素选择性。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/ai-guided-catalyst-turns-coe28282-and-waste-into-fertilizer-at-industrially-relevant-rates.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jun 2026 11:41:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/ai-guided-catalyst-turns-co%e2%82%82-and-waste-into-fertilizer-at-industrially-relevant-rates</guid></item><item><title>南极东部发现巨型扇形结构</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/giant-fan-shaped-structure-found-under-east-antarctica</link><description>包括我们地理系在内的一个国际研究小组发现了隐藏在东南极冰盖下方的巨大地质结构。研究结果是&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/giant-fan-shaped-structure-found-under-east-antarctica.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jun 2026 11:26:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/giant-fan-shaped-structure-found-under-east-antarctica</guid></item><item><title>氢能新突破将废热转化为清洁燃料</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/new-hydrogen-breakthrough-turns-waste-heat-into-clean-fuel</link><description>伯明翰大学的研究人员开发了一种新的低温制氢方法，可以使清洁燃料更便宜、更实用。该技术既可用于大型集中设施，也可用于利用主要工业运营废热的小型本地系统。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/new-hydrogen-breakthrough-turns-waste-heat-into-clean-fuel.webp" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jun 2026 11:11:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/new-hydrogen-breakthrough-turns-waste-heat-into-clean-fuel</guid></item></channel></rss>